- "gardeners and caretakers" refer to users with the roles "admin" and "editor";
- "flowers bloom" refers to the media assets in each category;
- "plots" refers to the combinations of categories and user roles.

- "Treasures" refer to media assets in the database;
- "Most beloved" indicates the media assets that are associated with the highest number of media assets in any category;
- "Hierarchy of categories" refers to the nested structure of categories, where each category can have a parent category.

